# Docs directory

All plans and docs for this project go in the `docs/` directory at the project root. When writing up a plan, design doc, or decision record, save it under `docs/` (with a descriptive filename, e.g. `2026-07-13-networking-plan.md`) rather than as an ad-hoc file elsewhere or only in chat.
